From b61b164858010c9d0dd7baaf554d11ab65aad4ed Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ci <ci@example.com>
Date: Mon, 4 May 2026 09:17:58 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Revert FusionOptimizer algorithm from PR #1615

Restore the pre-PR#1615 FusionOptimizer algorithm (backtracking with
deque-based subgraph expansion) in place of the bitset-based approach.

Only reverts the elemwise.py changes (the algorithm and
elemwise_to_scalar). Scalar/basic.py changes from the same PR are
not reverted as they are incompatible with the refactored Composite
class hierarchy on main.

Adapted for current imports (direct imports instead of ps.X aliases)
and post-PR changes (Composite without clone_graph, return_list=True).
